{
  "name": "Line Items",
  "description": "Standalone line item management endpoints for creating, reading, updating, and deleting line items (CORE/SUB classification, VAT, and automatic amount calculation). Line items can be created here and then linked to estimates, or created and linked in a single step via the Estimates API.",
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Create Line Item",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n    \"productCode\": \"SVC-001\",\n    \"productDescription\": \"Installation Service\",\n    \"additionalDetails\": \"Ground floor installation, requires 2 engineers\",\n    \"unitPrice\": 150.00,\n    \"coreOrSub\": \"CORE\",\n    \"quantity\": 2.0,\n    \"vatRate\": 0.20\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/line-items",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "line-items"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Create a new standalone line item for the authenticated user's company. The line item is not linked to any estimate on creation — use `POST /api/v1/estimates/{estimateId}/line-items` to create and link in one step, or `PUT /api/v1/estimates/{estimateId}/line-items/{lineItemId}` to link an existing line item.\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `productCode` (String): Short product or service code (e.g. `SVC-001`)\n- `productDescription` (String): Human-readable description of the product or service\n- `unitPrice` (BigDecimal): Price per unit, must be >= 0\n- `coreOrSub` (String enum): Classification — `CORE` for core work, `SUB` for subcontracted work\n- `quantity` (BigDecimal): Number of units, must be > 0\n- `vatRate` (BigDecimal): VAT rate as a decimal (e.g. `0.20` for 20%), must be >= 0\n\n**Optional fields:**\n- `additionalDetails` (String): Free-text additional context\n\n**Calculated fields (read-only in response):**\n- `netAmount` = `unitPrice` * `quantity`\n- `vatAmount` = `netAmount` * `vatRate`\n- `totalAmount` = `netAmount` + `vatAmount`\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"{{base_url}}/api/v1/line-items\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"productCode\": \"SVC-001\",\n    \"productDescription\": \"Installation Service\",\n    \"additionalDetails\": \"Ground floor installation, requires 2 engineers\",\n    \"unitPrice\": 150.00,\n    \"coreOrSub\": \"CORE\",\n    \"quantity\": 2.0,\n    \"vatRate\": 0.20\n  }'\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Create Line Item - Success",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"productCode\": \"SVC-001\",\n    \"productDescription\": \"Installation Service\",\n    \"additionalDetails\": \"Ground floor installation, requires 2 engineers\",\n    \"unitPrice\": 150.00,\n    \"coreOrSub\": \"CORE\",\n    \"quantity\": 2.0,\n    \"vatRate\": 0.20\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/line-items",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "line-items"
              ]
            }
          },
          "status": "Created",
          "code": 201,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"companyId\": 1,\n    \"productCode\": \"SVC-001\",\n    \"productDescription\": \"Installation Service\",\n    \"additionalDetails\": \"Ground floor installation, requires 2 engineers\",\n    \"unitPrice\": 150.00,\n    \"coreOrSub\": \"CORE\",\n    \"quantity\": 2.0000,\n    \"vatRate\": 0.2000,\n    \"netAmount\": 300.00,\n    \"vatAmount\": 60.00,\n    \"totalAmount\": 360.00,\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05T10:00:00\",\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-05T10:00:00\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
