        "description": "Permanently delete a line item. Due to `ON DELETE CASCADE` on the estimate-line item join table, deleting a line item also automatically removes it from any estimates it was linked to, and those estimates' totals will be recalculated on the next fetch.\n\n```bash\ncurl -X DELETE \"{{base_url}}/api/v1/line-items/1\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}\"\n```"
      },
